metadata.name: The Voyager
metadata.description:
“There is a way out of every box, a solution to every puzzle; it’s just a matter of finding it.”
―Captain Jean-Luc Picard

Nana Hank x DandyTron
The collaboration between DandyTron and myself consisted in interpreting existing artworks of the other in our own style and disciplines. "The Voyager" is a homage to Dandytron's genesis collection "Colors out of Space" with an added touch of nostalgic Star Trek vibe.

1/1 (3339 x 4683px, JPEG), 300 ppp, Adobe Photoshop
Germany (2022)
